DOC.brief_summary: The purpose of this study is to determine whether fenofibrate effects the toleration, safety, or efficacy biomarkers of CP-742,033, a drug being developed for the treatment of obesity.
DOC.brief_title: Effects of Fenofibrate on the Safety, Toleration and Efficacy Biomarkers of CP-742,033
DOC.criteria: BMI of 3040 kg/m2 Women of childbearing potential
